{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cause chaos with bombs to stop your opponents from winning as you plan your next move in this classic game with a twist.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bombs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are special bomb chips that have a chance to drop into play, using a bomb wipes a row of tokens! Use them to sneak a win or to stop your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Bomb.gif?t=1739310017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Freeze Chips</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ice chips do the opposite effect to bombs, they freeze a row of chips. To remove the frozen chips a player must use a turn to unfreeze a chip and remove them the next turn. Ice chips can provide strategic advantage but watch out your opponent may try doing the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Ice-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739310017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Plan and Strategize</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drop 4 has color indicators for each column so players can see the next incoming colored chip. This allows you to plan your strategy to win! Don't forget to keep an eye on your opponents incoming chips as they may be planning a win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Indicators.png?t=1739310017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Want to screw over an opponent or just wipe the board? Create combos by having more than one in a row and cause a chain reaction and columns will be wiped too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Combo.gif?t=1739310017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tiebreaker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find yourself in an intense long game? Be careful if you both get 4 in a line at the same time you cause a tiebreaker. Break your opponents 4 in a line to win, but watch out you may break your winning line too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Tiebreaker.gif?t=1739310017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Four To Win!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get four of your chips horizontally, vertically or diagonally to win. Plan and strategize to align your chips to win the match. Watch out though, your opponent will be doing the same! BONUS TIP: Frozen chips still count as getting 4 in a row to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/extras/Win4-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739310017\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739310017","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/page.bg.jpg?t=1739310017","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/6700cd81599746f4d0b3a8ce1ab583f57bb4f10b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739310017","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425120/6700cd81599746f4d0b3a8ce1ab583f57bb4f10b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739310017","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3502650,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cause chaos with bombs to stop your opponents from winning as you plan your next move in this classic game wit